TC-005: Verify Login with empty credentials

Precondition: User is on login page

Steps:

Leave Username field empty

Leave Password field empty

Click Login

Expected Result:
Error message is displayed indicating that username is required.

Status: Pass

TC-006: Verify Login with invalid credentials

Precondition: User is on login page

Steps:

Enter invalid username

Enter invalid password

Click Login

Expected Result:
System displays an error message stating that the username and password do not match any user.

Status: Pass

TC-007: Verify Login with locked-out user

Precondition: User is on login page

Steps:

Enter locked-out username

Enter valid password

Click Login

Expected Result:
System displays an error message indicating that the user is locked out.

Status: Pass

TC-008: Verify add-to-cart without user login

Precondition: User is not authenticated

Steps:

Navigate directly to the product listing page URL

Click Add to Cart button for any item

Expected Result:
User is redirected to the login page and item is not added to the cart.

Status: Pass

TC-009: Verify add-to-cart for the same item multiple times

Precondition: User is authenticated and viewing the item list page

Steps:

Select a product

Click Add to Cart button multiple times

Expected Result:
Item is added only once and cart count does not increase incorrectly.

Status: Pass

TC-010: Verify checkout with empty First Name

Precondition: User is authenticated and has items in the cart

Steps:

Navigate to My Cart page

Click Checkout

Leave First Name field empty

Enter valid Last Name and Postal Code

Click Continue

Expected Result:
Error message is displayed indicating that First Name is required and checkout does not proceed.

Status: Pass

TC-011: Verify checkout with empty Postal Code

Precondition: User is authenticated and has items in the cart

Steps:

Navigate to My Cart page

Click Checkout

Enter valid First Name and Last Name

Leave Postal Code empty

Click Continue

Expected Result:
Error message is displayed indicating that Postal Code is required and checkout is blocked.

Status: Pass

TC-012: Verify checkout with empty cart

Precondition: User is authenticated and cart is empty

Steps:

Navigate to My Cart page

Click Checkout

Expected Result:
System prevents checkout and displays a message indicating that the cart is empty.

Status: Pass

TC-013: Verify user session after logout

Precondition: User is logged in

Steps:

Click Logout

Press browser Back button

Expected Result:
User remains logged out and restricted pages are not accessible.

Status: Pass
